1
00:00:05,797 --> 00:00:08,622
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,622 --> 00:00:12,177
♫  Time has bear witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,177 --> 00:00:18,270
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,270 --> 00:00:24,596
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,596 --> 00:00:31,117
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,117 --> 00:00:36,103
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,103 --> 00:00:43,200
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:48,327
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,327 --> 00:00:49,840
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:55,603
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,603 --> 00:01:02,103
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:08,000
♫  With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,873
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:21,940 --> 00:01:24,207
Time to wake up, Gao Yang.

15
00:01:24,207 --> 00:01:26,486
Let me sleep a little longer.

16
00:01:28,180 --> 00:01:30,159
We're running late.

17
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:32,859
One more minute.

18
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:35,340
Gao Yang, answer the phone!

19
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:38,031
Answer the phone.

20
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:40,560
Answer the phone.

21
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,920
Gao Yang!

22
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:45,679
So annoying. It's right outside the window. You answer it.

23
00:01:45,679 --> 00:01:48,339
Gao Yang, answer the phone!

24
00:01:54,820 --> 00:01:57,480
Gao Yang! Gao Yang! The school is checking our dress code today.

25
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:59,859
Groom yourself a little, over.

26
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:04,938
- Okay.
- Who are you?

27
00:02:04,938 --> 00:02:06,759
Are you Gao Yang?

28
00:02:06,759 --> 00:02:07,820
No.

29
00:02:07,820 --> 00:02:10,579
Who are you? Don't move. I'm coming downstairs!

30
00:02:15,700 --> 00:02:18,079
Who's in there? Who...

31
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:20,760
Xiaowen. You're here?

32
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,860
I live here.

33
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:24,460
You live here?

34
00:02:24,460 --> 00:02:25,480
Since when?

35
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:26,800
Why didn't you tell me?

36
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:29,520
Why should we tell you about that?

37
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,960
Geez.

38
00:02:36,359 --> 00:02:38,020
Where's my breakfast?

39
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:40,319
You woke up late. It's gone.

40
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:41,939
Why didn't you wake me?

41
00:02:41,939 --> 00:02:44,179
How many times did I wake you?

42
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:48,340
Make me something then. I'm too hungry to move.

43
00:02:48,340 --> 00:02:49,900
Look at my eyes.

44
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:52,679
Get away from me. We're late, let's go to class.

45
00:02:52,679 --> 00:02:57,440
Why are you so mean? I'm grumpy when I wake up, I'm telling you.

46
00:02:57,440 --> 00:03:00,186
Gao Yang!

47
00:03:00,186 --> 00:03:02,167
Why are you still dragging your feet? Hurry up. We're going to be late.

48
00:03:02,167 --> 00:03:04,647
Let me change my underwear.

49
00:03:04,647 --> 00:03:05,499
Gao Yang!

50
00:03:05,499 --> 00:03:07,400
What are you doing? I'm changing!

51
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,500
I'm coming in!

52
00:03:10,740 --> 00:03:13,280
I'm just taking a look. Go away!

53
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,880
Go ahead, take a look.

54
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:16,678
Wait...

55
00:03:16,678 --> 00:03:19,180
Weren't you two...

56
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:22,314
Now you're living together?

57
00:03:24,260 --> 00:03:26,499
Well, that fight made us become friends.

58
00:03:26,499 --> 00:03:28,685
How long is he planning to stay?

59
00:03:29,379 --> 00:03:31,119
You two keep chatting. I'll wait for you outside.

60
00:03:31,119 --> 00:03:34,450
Buy me one boiled egg. I'll use it as a hot compress for my eyes.

61
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,339
What?

62
00:03:36,339 --> 00:03:38,140
How long is he planning to stay here?

63
00:03:38,140 --> 00:03:40,120
As long as he wants.

64
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:42,813
Gao Bin and I are sick of each other anyway.

65
00:03:42,813 --> 00:03:44,339
How are we going to call each other?

66
00:03:44,339 --> 00:03:46,380
What's the point of that phone?

67
00:03:46,380 --> 00:03:48,660
You're so loud. I can hear you when you speak normally.

68
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:51,380
Who said that?

69
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:54,580
What?

70
00:03:54,580 --> 00:03:56,287
What do you think?

71
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:02,080
- I'll ask my dad to get it back.
- I'll bend it then.

72
00:04:03,219 --> 00:04:04,939
Beibei, why aren't you talking?

73
00:04:04,939 --> 00:04:06,740
- I don't want to.
- That's nice.

74
00:04:06,740 --> 00:04:09,059
No, I have to speak.

75
00:04:09,059 --> 00:04:11,580
Gao Yang, don't you love to be a lone wolf?

76
00:04:11,580 --> 00:04:13,740
My brother wanted to go into your room and you refused.

77
00:04:13,740 --> 00:04:16,419
How come Ye Xiaowen can share a bunk bed with you?

78
00:04:16,419 --> 00:04:18,060
Is your brother the same as Xiaowen?

79
00:04:18,060 --> 00:04:20,900
Does your brother have a pretty relative like Mi Jia?

80
00:04:20,900 --> 00:04:23,339
My brother has me!

81
00:04:23,339 --> 00:04:26,339
Gao Yang, isn't it enough to have Wang Cailing?

82
00:04:26,339 --> 00:04:28,339
Wang Cailing is already in the past.

83
00:04:28,339 --> 00:04:31,020
It would be so inconvenient for me to visit you.

84
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:34,160
Why would it be inconvenient? We're all classmates.

85
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:37,020
Why don't you understand?

86
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:39,600
What should I understand?

87
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:44,639
It's so nice to be the only child.

88
00:04:44,639 --> 00:04:45,959
I envy you so much.

89
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:47,659
You had your own room since you were 6.

90
00:04:47,659 --> 00:04:50,720
You can have both drumsticks of a chicken.

91
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,242
When you shut the door, you can do whatever you want in there.

92
00:04:54,242 --> 00:04:57,480
[Episode 4]
[Unexpected New Life]

93
00:04:57,480 --> 00:05:00,220
Gao Yang!

94
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,539
Let's go.

95
00:05:01,539 --> 00:05:04,800
So, can we ask Mi Jia out to lunch today?

96
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,940
No.

97
00:05:05,940 --> 00:05:08,519
Don't treat me like a stranger. We're so close already.

98
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:11,299
I won't make fun of Mi Jia's stutter.

99
00:05:11,299 --> 00:05:12,979
All right. I'll stop talking.

100
00:05:12,979 --> 00:05:14,467
Stop talking about what?

101
00:05:14,467 --> 00:05:16,700
What are you two talking about?

102
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:18,500
Stay out of men's business.

103
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,759
I want to hear it.

104
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:22,840
Can't you know your place?

105
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,905
Go buy me breakfast!

106
00:05:32,050 --> 00:05:34,550
[Happy Place]

107
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:38,539
- Honey, I'm home.
- Final shot! Final shot! Final shot!

108
00:05:38,539 --> 00:05:40,440
Xiaowen is here again?

109
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,959
- Slam dunk!
- Final shot! Nice

110
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:44,360
- Slam dunk!
- Nice.

111
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:47,420
Go make us something to eat. Xiaowen and I are hungry. We still have to drink tonight.

112
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:49,600
We've been drinking all day. I'm getting a headache.

113
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,580
Beer won't go to your head. Just take a leak.

114
00:05:51,580 --> 00:05:55,480
Honey, why don't you drink another day?

115
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:04,940
My words don't count, right?

116
00:06:04,940 --> 00:06:06,480
The men are talking.

117
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,559
Women should stay out of it.

118
00:06:08,559 --> 00:06:09,879
Go do the laundry.

119
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:11,720
Clean up the bed in the bedroom.

120
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,519
Xiaowen is sleeping over tonight.

121
00:06:14,419 --> 00:06:16,720
Wait, where will Beibei sleep?

122
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,419
Let her sleep on the couch.

123
00:06:18,419 --> 00:06:20,335
No!

124
00:06:20,335 --> 00:06:21,620
What are you doing?

125
00:06:21,620 --> 00:06:24,099
Are you crazy? No, what?

126
00:06:25,779 --> 00:06:30,600
Mr. Wu, she said she can't let her grades slip anymore.

127
00:06:33,620 --> 00:06:35,460
It's good to have an ambition.

128
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:37,339
Improve yourself then.

129
00:06:37,339 --> 00:06:39,900
You're sitting by the best student in the class. Learn from her.

130
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:40,979
Okay.

131
00:06:40,979 --> 00:06:44,359
There's more. Don't be jumpy like that. You scared me.

132
00:06:44,359 --> 00:06:47,660
- Sit down.
- Thank you, Mr. Wu.

133
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:49,820
Let's talk about the essay theme.

134
00:06:54,620 --> 00:06:56,315
It's okay.

135
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:02,900
Mi Jia.

136
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:07,719
Don't run! Stop right there! Why did you run?

137
00:07:07,719 --> 00:07:10,639
You even put the hairpin on and we had dinner together.

138
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:12,680
Why are you being a stranger?

139
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,820
I...

140
00:07:13,820 --> 00:07:17,079
You... You... What do you want?

141
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:19,040
I want to ask you something.

142
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:21,560
What do you think of Gao Yang?

143
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:24,676
Don't think about it! Just answer with your instinct!

144
00:07:24,676 --> 00:07:26,920
I... I don't think much of him.

145
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,219
Good.

146
00:07:33,219 --> 00:07:35,299
Then we still have a chance to be besties.

147
00:07:35,299 --> 00:07:37,620
What about Ye Xiaowen? What's your relationship with him?

148
00:07:37,620 --> 00:07:40,539
No... no relations.

149
00:07:40,539 --> 00:07:44,319
Why isn't he staying in his own home instead of Gao Yang's home?

150
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,359
I... I have to go.

151
00:07:50,359 --> 00:07:53,419
I'm not done yet! Why did she run away again?

152
00:07:53,419 --> 00:07:56,198
Stop. Why are you two so mysterious?

153
00:07:58,060 --> 00:08:00,260
Your outfit...

154
00:08:00,260 --> 00:08:02,879
I... I am wearing the uniform.

155
00:08:02,879 --> 00:08:04,873
Why didn't you pull up the zipper?

156
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:14,580
Mi Jia, don't be so proud.

157
00:08:14,580 --> 00:08:16,720
Do you know who I am?

158
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,700
I'm the President of the Student Union.

159
00:08:18,700 --> 00:08:22,220
If you apologize to me, I won't write you up.

160
00:08:29,839 --> 00:08:33,860
Do you know how many people are competing to be my friend?

161
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:36,319
You won't say a word to me.

162
00:08:36,319 --> 00:08:38,190
You think you're special, huh?

163
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:41,379
She can wear it however she wants.

164
00:08:41,379 --> 00:08:42,699
What does it have to do with you?

165
00:08:42,699 --> 00:08:44,659
Jin Beibei, this is none of your business.

166
00:08:44,659 --> 00:08:46,819
She's my bestie.

167
00:08:46,819 --> 00:08:49,420
Her business is my business.

168
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:53,100
Mi Jia, you're friends with someone like this?

169
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:56,299
Let me tell you, my dad works at the TV station.

170
00:08:56,299 --> 00:08:59,040
The Learning Corner program on Tieyuan Channel 2, I'm the little host.

171
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:03,060
If you're friends with me, I can let you hold the mailbox.

172
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:04,980
Who cares about your stupid mailbox?

173
00:09:04,980 --> 00:09:06,380
You can't hold it even if you want to.

174
00:09:06,380 --> 00:09:08,599
I don't want to be on TV.

175
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:14,000
Do you hear that? She doesn't want to be on TV.

176
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,380
And you're still trying to show off.

177
00:09:18,539 --> 00:09:19,820
I'll write you up now.

178
00:09:19,820 --> 00:09:21,900
Go ahead. That's all you can do.

179
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:23,506
Let's go.

180
00:09:24,419 --> 00:09:26,133
Write it up nicely.

181
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:32,299
Mi Jia, tell me if she bullies you again. I'll protect you.

182
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,799
Thank... thank you.

183
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:38,020
Well, are we besties now?

184
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:40,994
What's going on with Ye Xiaowen?

185
00:09:47,459 --> 00:09:49,639
Mi Jia.

186
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:51,720
Mi Jia.

187
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:54,020
Jia Jia.

188
00:09:54,020 --> 00:09:54,939
Mi Jia.

189
00:09:54,939 --> 00:09:57,579
Beibei, I really can't tell you about Ye Xiaowen.

190
00:09:57,579 --> 00:10:01,859
Why? I won't ask about other things. I just want to know why they are so close.

191
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:05,020
He's not close to Gao Yang. He thinks Gao Yang is annoying.

192
00:10:05,020 --> 00:10:08,240
- That's not possible.
- It's true.

193
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,699
I'm not going.

194
00:10:09,699 --> 00:10:12,579
It's fun to do it together, right?

195
00:10:12,579 --> 00:10:14,640
Look!

196
00:10:15,860 --> 00:10:17,220
I'm dying to pee.

197
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:19,496
I've been holding it in for several classes.

198
00:10:21,980 --> 00:10:23,487
Are you scared?

199
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,842
Of what?

200
00:10:26,842 --> 00:10:28,700
Dong Dawei.

201
00:10:28,700 --> 00:10:30,579
You're scared to go to the restroom alone.

202
00:10:30,579 --> 00:10:34,679
You're right. From now on, you'll go to the restroom with me.

203
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:38,219
Can't you solve your conflict in the right way?

204
00:10:38,219 --> 00:10:40,399
Solve what?

205
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:43,299
Dong Dawei is a hillbilly. You can't talk any sense into him.

206
00:10:43,299 --> 00:10:45,179
He might not be that kind of person.

207
00:10:45,179 --> 00:10:46,957
Let's go.

208
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:58,420
I'm that kind of person.

209
00:10:58,420 --> 00:11:00,295
What did I say?

210
00:11:05,402 --> 00:11:09,024
[Beijing Roast Duck]

211
00:11:13,659 --> 00:11:15,260
You're still sleeping?

212
00:11:15,260 --> 00:11:17,700
What time is it now? Aren't you ashamed?

213
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:21,019
Let me ask you, what did you do last night?

214
00:11:21,019 --> 00:11:22,779
I couldn't find you all night.

215
00:11:22,779 --> 00:11:24,360
How many times did I tell you?

216
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,860
This is a group mission.

217
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:33,720
Nothing. I... I was reading the special Olympic charter all night.

218
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:36,179
While I was reading, I wanted to buy something for the family.

219
00:11:36,179 --> 00:11:38,579
I just went out for... a little while.

220
00:11:38,579 --> 00:11:40,180
For your son?

221
00:11:40,180 --> 00:11:42,099
Yes, yes. He loves roast duck.

222
00:11:42,099 --> 00:11:44,000
You're so good to your son.

223
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:47,120
Did you meet with the woman we told you about last time?

224
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,799
Who?

225
00:11:50,799 --> 00:11:53,820
She's from our No. 2 High School, the chemistry teacher Wang Lihua.

226
00:11:53,820 --> 00:11:55,957
Her husband passed away two years ago.

227
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:59,900
She... She didn't like me.

228
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:01,939
Why didn't she like you, Mr. Gao?

229
00:12:01,939 --> 00:12:05,939
If you dress up, you don't look like a 50-year-old at all.

230
00:12:07,299 --> 00:12:11,460
I'm in my 40s, early 40s.

231
00:12:11,460 --> 00:12:13,279
No wonder you look so young.

232
00:12:13,279 --> 00:12:15,380
Forty-year-old men are in their prime.

233
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:18,020
- Should I introduce a few more to you?
- No, that's all right.

234
00:12:18,020 --> 00:12:22,285
I... I want to focus on my job at the school first.

235
00:12:22,285 --> 00:12:24,120
Well, the Olympic Games are coming.

236
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,779
I want to make our track and field team stronger and better.

237
00:12:26,779 --> 00:12:29,259
That's what I need to do.

238
00:12:29,259 --> 00:12:31,093
Am I right, Vice Principal?

239
00:12:32,059 --> 00:12:33,624
Yes.

240
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:43,420
What a coincidence, Dawei.

241
00:12:43,420 --> 00:12:46,720
Well, if you have any problems with the school, you can tell me.

242
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,660
I know the principal really well.

243
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:50,740
Don't try to intimidate me with the principal.

244
00:12:50,740 --> 00:12:53,080
Didn't you say I can't get into a college?

245
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,679
I'm not afraid.

246
00:12:54,679 --> 00:12:56,140
No,

247
00:12:56,140 --> 00:12:58,840
I really don't want to fight you today.

248
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:01,220
I haven't had breakfast yet. I don't have any strength. It's true.

249
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:03,140
Watch this!

250
00:13:03,140 --> 00:13:05,151
Dong Dawei!

251
00:13:05,151 --> 00:13:08,340
I surrender. I surrender.

252
00:13:08,340 --> 00:13:11,299
I know about your beef with Mr. Gao. It has nothing to do with Gao Yang.

253
00:13:11,299 --> 00:13:14,579
Cut the crap! Come at me if you want.

254
00:13:18,100 --> 00:13:19,900
Why did you bring a weapon?

255
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:22,360
You have no martial arts ethics! You... you...

256
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,900
That's right.

257
00:13:28,900 --> 00:13:30,323
Hit me.

258
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:32,819
Hit him!

259
00:13:32,819 --> 00:13:36,180
Hit me. Hit me until you're satisfied.

260
00:13:42,819 --> 00:13:44,859
Your name is Ye Xiaowen, right?

261
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:48,217
I'll remember you.

262
00:13:50,539 --> 00:13:52,019
Remember him.

263
00:13:56,260 --> 00:13:59,451
- Let's go.
- What the hell? No martial arts ethics at all.

264
00:14:07,419 --> 00:14:09,579
Why didn't you hit him?

265
00:14:10,699 --> 00:14:12,980
Gao Yang, let me reiterate.

266
00:14:12,980 --> 00:14:17,880
I came here to study for college. If you cause any trouble again, I won't help you.

267
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,780
Don't put on that good student face with me.

268
00:14:19,780 --> 00:14:23,679
But you are surely fierce. No wonder Mi Jia likes to be with you.

269
00:14:23,679 --> 00:14:25,585
Can you teach me?

270
00:14:35,039 --> 00:14:37,800
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

271
00:14:46,940 --> 00:14:48,020
Excuse me.

272
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:49,528
Come in.

273
00:14:57,860 --> 00:15:00,419
You're late already. Hurry up!

274
00:15:01,980 --> 00:15:03,480
What's wrong with you?

275
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:05,575
Come on, look at the blackboard.

276
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:09,699
Why did you take so long in the restroom?

277
00:15:09,699 --> 00:15:10,960
Look at the blackboard.

278
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:14,020
We have three points, A, B, and C.

279
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:21,479
If we connect AB, BC, and AC, the three points will form a triangle of ABC...

280
00:15:21,479 --> 00:15:23,077
[Tieyuan Railway Station]

281
00:15:28,220 --> 00:15:31,740
Bin, you don't have to go back to school today.

282
00:15:31,740 --> 00:15:34,780
Finish that event report soon.

283
00:15:34,780 --> 00:15:36,579
Don't mess around.

284
00:15:36,579 --> 00:15:38,564
- I'm leaving now.
- Okay.

285
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:46,299
Is anyone going to No. 3 High School?

286
00:15:46,299 --> 00:15:49,100
No. 3 High School! Having a stroll, Bro?

287
00:15:49,100 --> 00:15:50,360
Are you going or not?

288
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:52,413
How much to go to No. 3 High School?

289
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:55,360
Twenty.

290
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,999
Are you crazy? I'm from Tieyuan.

291
00:15:57,999 --> 00:15:59,579
- 5 Yuan, Bro.
- 3 Yuan.

292
00:15:59,579 --> 00:16:01,533
Come on, get on.

293
00:16:07,399 --> 00:16:09,640
Isn't this Mr. Gao?

294
00:16:10,179 --> 00:16:11,499
Dawei's dad?

295
00:16:11,499 --> 00:16:13,740
- What a coincidence to run into you.
- Yes.

296
00:16:13,740 --> 00:16:16,000
- Forget it. I won't charge you.
- That's not right. Here, here.

297
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,840
No, we're all friends. Don't be a stranger. Enough with the formalities. Let's go.

298
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,399
Enough with the formalities. Let's go.

299
00:16:19,399 --> 00:16:21,710
- Thank you.
- It's nothing.

300
00:16:21,710 --> 00:16:24,260
[Brother Feng's BBQ]

301
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:31,640
Tor... tortoise.

302
00:16:31,640 --> 00:16:34,500
Go blow bubbles outside. You too. Play outside.

303
00:16:34,500 --> 00:16:37,240
Why are you all gathering around me? Can't you see I'm studying?

304
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:39,100
Let's go, Gao Yang. Let's go buy a torch ice cream.

305
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:42,079
It's my treat today.

306
00:16:42,079 --> 00:16:44,799
No, it's too windy outside.

307
00:16:45,819 --> 00:16:47,620
Gao Yang, what happened to you?

308
00:16:47,620 --> 00:16:50,020
You haven't moved for two periods.

309
00:16:50,740 --> 00:16:52,729
Are you sure you're okay?

310
00:16:52,729 --> 00:16:54,220
Why must I move?

311
00:16:54,220 --> 00:16:57,920
Look at the tortoises. They don't move at all. They can live so long.

312
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:59,120
What?

313
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,937
Tortoise.

314
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:04,579
Gao Yang is starting to ponder about life.

315
00:17:06,580 --> 00:17:08,300
Are you allowed to touch my head?

316
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:09,780
So what if I touched you?

317
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:12,460
As a man, you have to be steady and profound.

318
00:17:12,460 --> 00:17:14,340
You should know where you're from
and where you're going.

319
00:17:14,340 --> 00:17:16,387
Understand?

320
00:17:16,387 --> 00:17:18,480
Mucking around all day.

321
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,860
Gao Yang, Mr. Li wants to see you.

322
00:17:24,519 --> 00:17:28,099
Wait, what for? Can't he come and ask me in person?

323
00:17:28,099 --> 00:17:30,600
Gao Yang, how pompous of you.

324
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:32,100
Come out now!

325
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,688
That's for showing off.

326
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:45,100
But, Gao Yang, what exactly happened to you?

327
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:47,060
Why are you clenching your legs?

328
00:17:47,060 --> 00:17:50,340
A man must be mature and steady.

329
00:17:52,620 --> 00:17:54,219
These are the notes I made.

330
00:17:54,219 --> 00:17:56,220
Take it back and read it.

331
00:17:57,300 --> 00:18:01,340
Ask me if there's anything you don't understand.

332
00:18:01,340 --> 00:18:02,809
Okay.

333
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:13,983
Xiaowen, what's going on with you and Gao Yang?

334
00:18:13,983 --> 00:18:15,760
What do you mean?

335
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:20,839
I saw you two go to the restroom together.

336
00:18:20,839 --> 00:18:23,100
He pestered me to go with him.

337
00:18:23,100 --> 00:18:29,639
Didn't you say we transferred to this school to study for college and not to make friends?

338
00:18:29,639 --> 00:18:31,900
He's not my friend.

339
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:34,403
All right.

340
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:41,780
You shouldn't fight with Dong Dawei like last time.

341
00:18:41,780 --> 00:18:48,359
If we get expelled because of fighting, wouldn't that wipe out our previous efforts?

342
00:18:48,359 --> 00:18:53,070
You know we're not just going to college for ourselves.

343
00:18:56,430 --> 00:19:01,280
- Well, I'm heading back now.
- Okay.

344
00:19:05,519 --> 00:19:07,419
Old Li, why don't we take a rain check?

345
00:19:07,419 --> 00:19:08,860
Why?

346
00:19:08,860 --> 00:19:11,559
Is there a problem with a pull-up test?

347
00:19:13,259 --> 00:19:15,520
The problem is quite serious.

348
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:19,040
You always have so many ideas.

349
00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:23,719
I'm telling you, I only let you be the Sports Commissary because of your dad.

350
00:19:23,719 --> 00:19:25,300
I didn't want that.

351
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:26,979
Why don't you remove me from the post?

352
00:19:26,979 --> 00:19:28,620
Go notify the students to come to class.

353
00:19:28,620 --> 00:19:30,600
Enough with the useless ideas.

354
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:45,500
[Sophmore Class 3]

355
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:27,975
Genius.

356
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:33,119
Well, there will be a pull-up test in PE later!

357
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:39,239
She really isn't talking to anyone.

358
00:20:39,239 --> 00:20:41,960
Pretty girls are always aloof and reserved.

359
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:12,240
Hello, Classmate.

360
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:16,039
Can I borrow this notebook?

361
00:21:30,019 --> 00:21:33,499
This is my name, Piao Jiutong.

362
00:21:33,499 --> 00:21:37,279
From now on, we know each other.

363
00:21:37,279 --> 00:21:41,360
But... But... that's not my notebook.

364
00:21:46,739 --> 00:21:49,140
I didn't do it on purpose.

365
00:21:49,140 --> 00:21:53,459
Should I... buy you another one?

366
00:21:58,300 --> 00:22:01,860
Are you a bad... bad student?

367
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:06,626
This is just a sticker.

368
00:22:08,179 --> 00:22:10,380
I'm a really nice guy.

369
00:22:10,380 --> 00:22:12,599
If you need to buy anything, you can come to me.

370
00:22:12,599 --> 00:22:14,659
I'll give you a discount.

371
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:18,300
Dawei's dad, weren't you a bus driver before?

372
00:22:18,300 --> 00:22:20,359
Why aren't you driving a bus now?

373
00:22:20,359 --> 00:22:22,200
I want to,

374
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:24,860
but the bus company fired me.

375
00:22:27,860 --> 00:22:29,140
Why?

376
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:31,839
The company wasn't doing well and they were laying people off.

377
00:22:31,839 --> 00:22:34,200
I had an incident a few years ago.

378
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:36,419
I smashed a girl's head with the door.

379
00:22:36,419 --> 00:22:38,719
They fired me because of that.

380
00:22:38,719 --> 00:22:42,720
I don't have a choice. I have to make a living. After that, I opened a repair shop.

381
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:46,619
In my free time, I would drive the minibus and make some extra money.

382
00:22:46,619 --> 00:22:48,791
It was a coincidence that I ran into you today.

383
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:56,160
Mr. Gao, I remember you used to coach the soccer team. Do you still do that?

384
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:58,800
Something came up at home and I've quit it ever since.

385
00:22:58,800 --> 00:23:00,820
How's Dawei's arm?

386
00:23:00,820 --> 00:23:02,959
Nothing serious.

387
00:23:02,959 --> 00:23:04,780
He can't do any heavy lifting,

388
00:23:04,780 --> 00:23:06,979
but it doesn't keep him from doing much else.

389
00:23:06,979 --> 00:23:08,576
It's okay.

390
00:23:10,259 --> 00:23:12,419
Dawei's dad.

391
00:23:12,419 --> 00:23:15,599
The school has its own rules.

392
00:23:15,599 --> 00:23:17,240
I really couldn't keep him back then.

393
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:20,299
Don't say that. You're making it seem like I'm blaming you.

394
00:23:20,299 --> 00:23:22,219
That was all his fault.

395
00:23:22,219 --> 00:23:24,100
He even dared to fight others.

396
00:23:24,100 --> 00:23:25,880
Why didn't they kick out anyone else?

397
00:23:25,880 --> 00:23:30,960
Besides, without your help, he wouldn't even be accepted into No. 3 High School.

398
00:23:30,960 --> 00:23:33,780
How is Dawei doing in school? The college entrance exam is around the corner.

399
00:23:33,780 --> 00:23:36,019
Don't mention his grades. They're terrible.

400
00:23:36,019 --> 00:23:37,599
We're not counting on him to do well on the exam.

401
00:23:37,599 --> 00:23:39,900
In the future, he'll just learn to drive with me.

402
00:23:39,900 --> 00:23:43,400
Don't say that. How do you know he won't make it?

403
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:46,139
He's an athlete. His grades were always bad.

404
00:23:46,139 --> 00:23:49,880
Now, he can't play soccer anymore. What can he do besides drive with me?

405
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:52,520
Don't mention him. I get so pissed off when I talk about him.

406
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:55,780
How's your son doing?

407
00:23:55,780 --> 00:23:57,140
What grade is he in now?

408
00:23:57,140 --> 00:23:59,119
He's a sophomore now. He's still the same.

409
00:23:59,119 --> 00:24:02,959
If Dawei is in the same class with him, they might become really good friends.

410
00:24:02,959 --> 00:24:04,309
Yes.

411
00:24:10,259 --> 00:24:14,159
Brother Dawei, that Ye Xiaowen is quite arrogant.

412
00:24:14,159 --> 00:24:16,140
Why didn't you beat him up?

413
00:24:16,140 --> 00:24:18,540
Beat him up? You go ahead.

414
00:24:18,540 --> 00:24:21,799
But... That guy seems to have some skills.

415
00:24:21,799 --> 00:24:23,568
I'm no match for him.

416
00:24:23,568 --> 00:24:25,559
The point is, he was able to snap that thick broomstick.

417
00:24:25,559 --> 00:24:28,719
- Exactly.
- Brother Dawei, we should be careful.

418
00:24:31,351 --> 00:24:33,454
Come on.

419
00:24:36,540 --> 00:24:38,999
Why would I want your money? Homework!

420
00:24:38,999 --> 00:24:40,759
I... I didn't do my homework.

421
00:24:40,759 --> 00:24:42,120
Why didn't you?

422
00:24:42,120 --> 00:24:45,310
Why should I do it? What's the point of it?

423
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:47,119
How many times did you repeat school?

424
00:24:47,119 --> 00:24:48,799
Both of you are older than me.

425
00:24:48,799 --> 00:24:50,840
Is it an honor to be my minion?

426
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:53,159
Brother Dawei, what about your homework?

427
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,359
Let us borrow it.

428
00:24:54,359 --> 00:24:55,652
- Let us borrow it.
- Exactly.

429
00:24:56,152 --> 00:24:57,400
I didn't do it.

430
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:59,440
Then why were you on our case about it?

431
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:03,039
Dawei wants Wanwan to teach him how to do it.

432
00:25:03,039 --> 00:25:05,659
Wanwan is a good tutor.

433
00:25:08,039 --> 00:25:11,520
Dong Dawei. What are you doing?

434
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,680
Why aren't you in class?

435
00:25:13,680 --> 00:25:16,240
I... I'm just about to go to class.

436
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:21,540
Wanwan, well, are you still tutoring me after school?

437
00:25:21,540 --> 00:25:23,319
Depends on my schedule.

438
00:25:23,319 --> 00:25:26,055
- "Are you still tutoring me after school?"
- "Depends on my schedule."

439
00:25:31,699 --> 00:25:34,140
Xiaowen, how are your pull-ups?

440
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:37,780
I can do 20 forehand pull-ups and 30 backhand pull-ups.

441
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:41,618
What are you doing? This is my new look. Don't touch it.

442
00:25:41,618 --> 00:25:43,939
Gao Yang, you're moving now?

443
00:25:43,939 --> 00:25:45,659
- What are you listening to?
- This is art. You won't understand.

444
00:25:45,659 --> 00:25:46,799
- Let me hear it.
- You won't understand.

445
00:25:46,799 --> 00:25:48,380
Let me hear it! I don't understand?

446
00:25:48,380 --> 00:25:52,120
This is art. How can you understand...

447
00:25:52,120 --> 00:25:54,799
Why are you two still playing over there?

448
00:25:54,799 --> 00:25:57,560
- Time for class.
- Hurry up, go to class.

449
00:25:57,560 --> 00:26:01,419
Girls, walk faster! Why aren't you energetic for PE class?

450
00:26:02,620 --> 00:26:05,000
Mr. Li, we have full attendance for Class 3.

451
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:07,179
Ready for your inspection!

452
00:26:10,455 --> 00:26:11,860
What's with your jacket?

453
00:26:11,860 --> 00:26:13,699
- I'm hot.
- Hot?

454
00:26:13,699 --> 00:26:15,739
Take it off and put it aside then.

455
00:26:15,739 --> 00:26:17,439
It's too dirty, Mr. Li.

456
00:26:17,439 --> 00:26:19,142
Let's begin.

457
00:26:20,459 --> 00:26:24,499
For girls, do arm suspension for at least 30 seconds to pass.

458
00:26:24,499 --> 00:26:29,019
For boys, do at least ten forehand pull-ups to pass.

459
00:26:29,019 --> 00:26:30,400
- That's too many. We can't do it.
- It's easy.

460
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:31,839
We can't do it.

461
00:26:31,839 --> 00:26:34,540
Don't complain. It's the same for everybody.

462
00:26:34,540 --> 00:26:37,620
Zhao Jiabao, you go first.

463
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:44,319
Mr. Li, can I skip the test?

464
00:26:44,319 --> 00:26:45,419
What do you think?

465
00:26:45,419 --> 00:26:47,128
Hurry up.

466
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:51,709
Piece of cake.

467
00:27:03,620 --> 00:27:06,160
Mr. Li, I really can't do it. Why don't I do an arm suspension instead?

468
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:08,955
That's for girls. Are you a girl?

469
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:13,320
Fine.

470
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,900
I'm willing to be a girl.

471
00:27:19,620 --> 00:27:21,219
Get down.

472
00:27:21,219 --> 00:27:23,799
Gao Yang, demonstrate it for him.

473
00:27:23,799 --> 00:27:25,424
Okay.

474
00:27:32,079 --> 00:27:36,040
One, two, three...

475
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:47,860
You haven't finished ten of them yet.

476
00:27:47,860 --> 00:27:49,700
Go for it, Gao Yang!

477
00:27:49,700 --> 00:27:51,780
Mr. Li, my pants...

478
00:27:51,780 --> 00:27:53,903
My jacket is coming loose.

479
00:27:55,188 --> 00:27:57,840
- I've been putting up with you for a long time, I told you to...

480
00:27:57,840 --> 00:28:01,260
Mr. Li, don't do that! Mr. Li! Don't, don't! Don't do that!

481
00:28:01,260 --> 00:28:03,094
Mr. Li,

482
00:28:04,820 --> 00:28:06,240
I'm not feeling well.

483
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:08,217
I want to go to the health clinic.

484
00:28:09,599 --> 00:28:11,540
Find a classmate to go with you.

485
00:28:11,540 --> 00:28:13,019
I want Gao Yang to go with me.

486
00:28:13,019 --> 00:28:14,820
You want Gao Yang?

487
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:19,680
Go on, go on.

488
00:28:19,680 --> 00:28:21,820
Come back soon.

489
00:28:21,820 --> 00:28:23,289
Zhao Jiabao,

490
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:25,809
keep going.

491
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:31,760
Wait, why did come to the restroom? Aren't you going to the health clinic?

492
00:28:35,900 --> 00:28:38,559
Wait, what are you doing?

493
00:28:38,559 --> 00:28:39,879
- Take if off.
- Take what off?

494
00:28:39,879 --> 00:28:43,101
- Take off your pants.
- Why should I take off my pants?

495
00:28:43,101 --> 00:28:44,559
- I saw everything.
- What did you see?

496
00:28:44,559 --> 00:28:45,799
What did you see?

497
00:28:45,799 --> 00:28:47,719
Take them off now.

498
00:28:59,759 --> 00:29:01,659
Get up. Get up!

499
00:29:01,659 --> 00:29:03,659
What are you doing? Looking at lottery tickets again?

500
00:29:03,659 --> 00:29:05,839
You bought so many of them. Have you ever won anything?

501
00:29:05,839 --> 00:29:06,880
Get up! Get up now!

502
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,360
What are you doing?

503
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:10,559
Why didn't you report to me after you came back?

504
00:29:10,559 --> 00:29:13,559
I'm tired from taking the train all day.

505
00:29:13,559 --> 00:29:15,459
You're tired? Go home then.

506
00:29:15,459 --> 00:29:17,979
Your two boys are waiting for you at home.

507
00:29:21,799 --> 00:29:23,060
Isn't this a great move?

508
00:29:23,060 --> 00:29:26,210
- What move?
- No move is the best move.

509
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,108
Think about it.

510
00:29:28,108 --> 00:29:31,559
I went to Beijing, taught Anna a lesson,

511
00:29:31,559 --> 00:29:34,379
and let Gao Yang and Xiaowen get close to each other.

512
00:29:34,379 --> 00:29:36,200
Two birds with one stone.

513
00:29:36,200 --> 00:29:39,240
If I'm home, Gao Yang would certainly make a scene.

514
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:44,739
If I'm not home, they might gradually get along and become friends.

515
00:29:45,319 --> 00:29:47,780
Isn't that brilliant?

516
00:29:48,559 --> 00:29:51,540
So brilliant.

517
00:29:51,540 --> 00:29:57,479
You went in hiding while the Monkey King and Prince Nezha treated me like the Dragon King. Did you know that?

518
00:29:57,479 --> 00:30:00,920
Gao Bin, ever since your divorce,

519
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:03,519
I've been so worried, you know?

520
00:30:03,519 --> 00:30:08,120
You don't cook or do laundry and you just hide yourself in the equipment room.

521
00:30:08,120 --> 00:30:11,760
Your son Gao Yang eats at least two out of three meals at my house every day. Did you know that?

522
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:14,000
Why are you bringing that up? What kind of relationship do we have?

523
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:16,539
- Can't I just vent off a little?
- Sure, you can.

524
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:22,920
Did you buy that Beijing Roast Duck at the train station?

525
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:24,640
It's not authentic, you know?

526
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:26,420
What are you doing here?

527
00:30:27,599 --> 00:30:29,480
Where are the materials you got from Beijing?

528
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:43,759
You like Mickey Mouse?

529
00:30:43,759 --> 00:30:45,279
Who likes Mickey Mouse?

530
00:30:45,279 --> 00:30:47,200
Gao Bin bought it for me.

531
00:30:48,820 --> 00:30:53,720
You're an interesting fellow. Who would bring needles and thread to school? Are you the Invincible Eastern Swordsman?

532
00:30:56,860 --> 00:30:58,160
Well, sew it up quickly.

533
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,440
Class will be over soon.

534
00:30:59,440 --> 00:31:01,105
It's embarrassing.

535
00:31:02,839 --> 00:31:04,319
You're afraid of being embarrassed?

536
00:31:04,319 --> 00:31:05,839
You're the embarrassing one.

537
00:31:05,839 --> 00:31:07,240
How am I embarrassing?

538
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:11,260
You're a man who's sewing pants.

539
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:14,751
Shut up.

540
00:31:20,599 --> 00:31:22,640
Not bad.

541
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:25,055
Hasn't Mr. Gao ever sewn pants for you?

542
00:31:27,119 --> 00:31:29,599
Sew pants for me?

543
00:31:29,599 --> 00:31:34,079
If he knows I split my pants, he would beat me up.

544
00:31:34,540 --> 00:31:36,179
Why?

545
00:31:36,820 --> 00:31:38,585
That's how he is.

546
00:31:39,640 --> 00:31:42,840
Since I was a child, he's thought it was me who caused all the trouble.

547
00:31:42,840 --> 00:31:46,759
If someone beat me up, I must be the one who started it.

548
00:31:46,759 --> 00:31:49,959
If I didn't do well on a test, it must be because I didn't review very hard.

549
00:31:49,959 --> 00:31:53,040
If a little girl is crying, it must be my fault.

550
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:55,440
Anyway, everything is my fault.

551
00:32:03,019 --> 00:32:06,480
You should tell Mr. Gao about your conflict with Dong Dawei.

552
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:08,570
It's not your fault.

553
00:32:10,559 --> 00:32:11,559
What?

554
00:32:11,559 --> 00:32:13,699
It's not your fault.

555
00:32:14,620 --> 00:32:16,359
That's not important.

556
00:32:16,359 --> 00:32:20,040
I'm his son after all. It doesn't matter.

557
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:24,159
- But you and Dong Dawei...
- All right, let's go.

558
00:32:24,159 --> 00:32:26,173
I'll buy you a torch ice cream.

559
00:32:31,780 --> 00:32:34,878
How many times have I explained this and you're still getting it wrong?

560
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:37,620
I'll explain it one last time.

561
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:39,656
This is the last time.

562
00:32:39,656 --> 00:32:41,286
Listen carefully.

563
00:32:41,820 --> 00:32:46,859
Okay, let's say the power function FX increases monotonically in the first quadrant.

564
00:32:46,859 --> 00:32:49,519
Now, let's set a and b,

565
00:32:49,519 --> 00:32:52,599
a for 0-0, b for 1-1...

566
00:33:00,340 --> 00:33:02,161
Listen to me!

567
00:33:04,519 --> 00:33:07,619
Hey, who do you think is better, Hong Qigong or Ouyang Feng?

568
00:33:07,619 --> 00:33:10,979
I think Wanwan is the best.

569
00:33:11,900 --> 00:33:17,259
The 2nd and 3rd quadrant images are determined based on the parity.

570
00:33:17,259 --> 00:33:21,899
We have a sample here. When α is less than 0, Y equals Xα.

571
00:33:21,899 --> 00:33:23,523
In that case, we...

572
00:33:26,195 --> 00:33:29,419
[Principal's Office]

573
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:34,359
It's great to be a superior after all.

574
00:33:35,820 --> 00:33:37,779
The tea is so aromatic.

575
00:33:37,779 --> 00:33:39,640
The office is bright and spacious too.

576
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:41,171
It's so nice.

577
00:33:41,799 --> 00:33:42,759
Come on.

578
00:33:42,759 --> 00:33:44,760
I cooled it for you. Drink it.

579
00:33:50,039 --> 00:33:51,920
Bin, how about this?

580
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:55,400
You should strive to be a principal too.

581
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:58,419
I know you're the principal. Stop bragging.

582
00:33:58,419 --> 00:34:01,120
All right, Mr. Principal. I'm leaving if there's nothing else.

583
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:03,540
Wait, come back here.

584
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:12,179
Shouldn't you prepare something for the National High School Students Sports Games?

585
00:34:12,179 --> 00:34:15,200
Why don't you bring our soccer team together again?

586
00:34:15,200 --> 00:34:16,499
I'll pass.

587
00:34:16,499 --> 00:34:19,500
Xiaowen just arrived. I don't have time for that.

588
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:22,280
Mr. Gao, you're not just a parent.

589
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:24,840
You're also a teacher, you know?

590
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:28,239
Old Jin, I don't like what you're saying.

591
00:34:28,239 --> 00:34:30,719
I'm also bringing honor to the school by taking care of Xiaowen.

592
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:35,899
Besides, Xiaowen and Mi Jia are perfectly capable of passing the provincial qualification competition.

593
00:34:35,899 --> 00:34:40,820
When they get a rank at the national competitions, wouldn't that be your achievement too?

594
00:34:40,820 --> 00:34:42,260
Knock it off.

595
00:34:42,260 --> 00:34:44,539
The entire nation is preparing for the Olympic Games now.

596
00:34:44,539 --> 00:34:46,820
Our school has to improve our sports achievements too.

597
00:34:46,820 --> 00:34:50,839
You can't just coach Xiaowen and Mi Jia.

598
00:34:50,839 --> 00:34:52,260
I've made a decision.

599
00:34:52,260 --> 00:34:54,700
You will be the coach of the track and field team of No. 3 High School.

600
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:56,780
- No, I'm not.
- Yes, you are.

601
00:34:56,780 --> 00:34:58,660
You will be the coach. I've made my decision!

602
00:34:58,660 --> 00:35:01,419
Weren't you good at all track and field events while you were in college?

603
00:35:01,419 --> 00:35:03,780
Well, show me some good results.

604
00:35:03,780 --> 00:35:05,380
What's the Olympic spirit?

605
00:35:05,380 --> 00:35:08,140
The most important thing is participation.

606
00:35:08,140 --> 00:35:09,800
Don't take winning too seriously.

607
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:14,759
I'll fire you if you keep up with that nonsense!

608
00:35:18,539 --> 00:35:21,040
Old Jin, you're...

609
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:22,900
Don't get upset.

610
00:35:22,900 --> 00:35:25,042
You're...

611
00:35:25,042 --> 00:35:27,580
Let's give that matter some further thought.

612
00:35:27,580 --> 00:35:29,440
It's just that Xiaowen just arrived.

613
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:32,059
I still haven't figured out how to get along with him yet.

614
00:35:32,059 --> 00:35:34,840
Let me figure that out first.

615
00:35:34,840 --> 00:35:36,519
You should... take it easy.

616
00:35:36,519 --> 00:35:38,731
Take it easy.

617
00:35:38,731 --> 00:35:39,920
Wait!

618
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:43,339
What's wrong with you, Old Jin? I told you we should give that matter some further thought.

619
00:35:45,199 --> 00:35:50,100
Did you get to see Anna when you were in Beijing?

620
00:35:50,100 --> 00:35:51,619
Yes, I did.

621
00:35:51,619 --> 00:35:52,979
Didn't I call you?

622
00:35:52,979 --> 00:35:55,319
I told you I scolded her. Did you forget?

623
00:35:55,319 --> 00:35:58,139
Stop fooling me. Anna called me.

624
00:35:58,139 --> 00:35:59,774
What did she say?

625
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:11,740
She said she wanted to transfer your son to another school.

626
00:36:11,740 --> 00:36:13,459
What did you say?

627
00:36:13,459 --> 00:36:16,660
I told Anna that Gao Yang is in the critical high school phase now.

628
00:36:16,660 --> 00:36:20,879
A frequent change of environment isn't good for him.

629
00:36:20,879 --> 00:36:22,619
How did she reply?

630
00:36:22,619 --> 00:36:26,239
She said she would ask Gao Yang.

631
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:44,060
Bin, you should put Xiaowen's matter aside for now.

632
00:36:44,060 --> 00:36:46,460
Think about it,

633
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:52,761
if Gao Yang really leaves Tieyuan, what would be left between the two of you?

